data.description: WOW!!! BEST DEAL IN VERONAWALK NEW ROOF  3 bedrooms with den/two bath original DiVosta poured concrete, Oakmont single family home located in the gated community of VeronaWalk. A screened foyer leads to your glass entry door. Before you lies an open floorplan with lofty ceilings and a flooring mix of tile and Bella Cero engineered wood. A centrally located kitchen has shaker style cabinetry with full extension slide out drawers in the pantry and cabinets. The Frigidaire refrigerator was purchased in 2023 and the GE range was installed in 2021. An under sink three stage water filtration with goose neck faucet is a plus. So many upgrades have been added including new tile roof/gutters(2023), exterior house painted (2022), repainted garage walls and epoxy floor (2023), newer Lennox A/C (2020), insignia washing machine and accordion hurricane shutters/panels. Custom-built cabinets and a desk are in the den as well as an entertainment wall unit with installed speakers. Some rooms have crown molding/chair rail and windows have custom treatments. From the rear bank of sliding glass doors, you exit onto a covered lanai with a freshly screened (2023) enclosed extended patio overlooking water.
